AiDbg combines a Cheat Engine-style memory scanner with a local AI agent      
that doesn't just find your offsets — it writes the code for you.
Autonomous. Fast. Runs entirely on your machine.                              
                                                                                
This is what reverse engineering looks like when AI does the work.
